<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Confirm Your Account</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #691f74;
      --primary-color-dark: #44195d; 
      --body-background-color: #f4f4f4;
      --text-color: #333;
      --text-light-color: #666;
    }
    @font-face {
      font-family: 'Poppins';
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 400;
      src: local('Poppins Regular'), local('Poppins-Regular'), url(https://fonts.gstatic.com/s/poppins/v15/pxiByp8kv8JHgFVrLDz8Z1xlFQ.woff2) format('woff2');
    }
    /* Add your styles here */
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      border: #333;
    }
    .banner {
      background-color: #44195d;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: white;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    h2 {
      color: #333;
    }
    a {
      color: #691f74;
    }
    p {
      color: #333;
      opacity: 0.8;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 16px 26px;
      font-weight: 600;
      background-color: #691f74;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 35px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #44195d;
    }
     /* Social icons */
   .social-icons {
      margin-top: 30px;
     text-align: center;
    }
    .social-icons a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 10px;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .fa-linkedin {
      color: #0A66C2;
    }
    .fa-facebook {
      color: #0866FF;
    }
    .fa-github {
      color: #010409;
    }
    .fa-twitter {
      color: #1D9BF0;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="banner"> 
      <h1>Welcome to Jobster</h1>
    </div>
    <h2>Confirm Your Account</h2>
    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>Welcome to Jobster! We're thrilled to have you on board. </br>
      To get started, please click the button below to confirm your email address:</p>
    <a href="<%= confirmationURL %>" class="btn" style="color: #fff;">Confirm Account</a>
    <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can also confirm your account by copying and pasting the following link into your browser:</p>
    <a href="<%= confirmationURL %>" style="color: #691f74;"><%= confirmationURL %></a>
    <p>Thank you for choosing Jobster. </br> If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at support@jobster.com</p>

 <!-- Social icons -->
    <div class="social-icons">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-linkedin"></i></a>
      <a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-github"></i></a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-facebook"></i></a>
      <a href="https://twitter.com/" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-twitter"></i></a>
    </div>
  </div>

<script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/your-fontawesome-kit-id.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
